The '''Wilderness Rogues' Chests''' are located at the [[Rogues' Castle]] at approximately level 54 [[Wilderness]]. A [[Thieving]] level of 84 is required to open these chests. Upon successfully unlocking a chest, the player is granted 100 [[experience]] and various treasures including noted [[fish]], [[runes]], [[ores]], and noted [[dragonstone]]s. Each chest is worth 2,000 [[coins]] on average.

