==Getting to them==
A player has many options to get to the Rogues' Chests.
*Teleporting using a [[Wilderness Obelisk]] is the fastest method to get there. It is recommended to have completed the [[hard Wilderness Diary]] in order to teleport directly to the level 50 obelisk.
*Players are able to use the [[Annakarl Teleport]] or an [[Annakarl teleport|Annakarl teleport tablet]] from the [[Grand Exchange]]. This teleports the player relatively close to the castle, though slightly further than the Wilderness Obelisk.
*Teleporting to Fountain of rune using the [[Wilderness sword]] 3 (one daily teleport) or 4 (unlimited). This is similar distance as the Annakarl Teleport.
*Players may also use the [[Lever (Edgeville)|Edgeville lever]] to teleport deep in the [[Wilderness]] and run east to the [[Rogues' Castle]]. However, doing this requires the player to run past the [[Chaos Elemental]], which hits consistently, even at high levels.

