The castle is home to many non-aggressive level-135 [[rogue]]s. Once a chest is opened, however, these rogues will become alerted to the players presence and begin to attack. As such it is '''highly recommended''' to have a [[Prayer]] level of at least 43 to use [[Protect from Melee]], as the rogues have a max hit of 15. Low-cost or untradeable equipment that provides a high [[Prayer bonus]] such as a set of [[monk's robes]], a [[holy symbol]], any [[god book]]s, any [[Ardougne cloak]]s, and the [[Explorer's ring]], are recommended as they can easily be re-obtained. A possible setup is shown on the right. 

'''As the chests are located very deep within the Wilderness, beware of [[player-killer]]s! In addition, use caution when entering or leaving the area, as the [[Chaos Elemental]] may wander in front or near the Rogues' Castle! Do not bring items you are unwilling to lose.'''

